Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:23.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kaiji: Tatsuya Fujiwara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:26.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They face off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:28.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Interview: Tatsuya Fujiwara x Masato Hagiwara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:31.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These two have put all their hearts into playing Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:35.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,About Kaiji himself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:38.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's pretty much a loser. Yep, a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:40.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:47.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's great at coming up with things, but that just isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:49.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He gets out of one mess and he's right back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:53.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm him in the anime and Tatsuya's him in the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:57.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you could play the Bog in real life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:00:59.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nope, not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:02.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Each shot is what, 4,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:05.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:09.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji challenges the monster machine in theaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:13.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji 2: Jinsei Dakkai Game, this November 5th!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:20.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打ち続けるカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:20.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji keeps shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:25.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この物量作戦が呼ぶ奇跡 僥倖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:23.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is a war of materiel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:25.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then, a fortuitous miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:27.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１段目 ２段目に続き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:33.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not only are the first and second trays clogged, but also the third!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:32.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３段目の外れ穴の排出口の管が\N詰まったのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:43.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！決めろ！決めちまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:43.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go! Finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:46.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけー！\Nカイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:46.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:48.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His prayers were answered!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:48.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,満願成就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:52.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But in the very moment when everyone thought he'd won...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:53.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが誰もがそう思った その瞬間！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,割れる　割れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:57.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They shatter. They shatter! They shatter!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:57.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,割れる！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:04.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はねつけた　またしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:06.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He was repelled! Repelled again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:06.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はねつけた！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:12.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)\pos(640,505)}Spiraling Silver Spheres
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:14.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ 今の…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What just happened!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:16.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はね返したぞ　縁で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:16.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Something blocked him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:18.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？なんで外れる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How'd that miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:19.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウソだろ？あんなん ありかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:40.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外れ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:39.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:43.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外れって…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:42.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He missed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:46.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セーフだったのか 今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:46.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:57.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遅くなりました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:56.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry it took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:00.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,む… 村上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Murakami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:04.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　ここに着いたら\Nピンチでしたので 指示を待たず
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:06.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We saw what was happening, so we went ahead and started it up without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:08.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ともかく作動させました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつを\Nおおっ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,See, we found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,長く使ってませんでしたから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:17.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, so I wasn't sure if it would work, but it seems like it was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:16.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きちんと作動するかどうか\N不安だったのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:18.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題ないようです\N電気系も大丈夫な…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The wiring looks like it's fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貸せ！\Nあっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:19.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:29.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった！これで生き残れる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:29.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm gonna survive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:34.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう何発 来ようと何の問題もない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:33.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how many balls you shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll block every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべて はね返せる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:41.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Around that hole is a ring of tiny jet nozzles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,穴の周りに\Nびっしりと敷き詰められた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:42.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,極小の噴出口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこから噴射される強風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:47.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This barrier of wind will block everything shot at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この風のバリアで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! What's happening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:58.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かんねえ\N分かんねえが大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:57.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玉はクルーンにあふれている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:00.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The tray is full of balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:04.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだまだ３段目には送れる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:03.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And more are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,送れるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:05.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:16.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題ねえ！吹き飛ばせる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:17.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter! I'll blow by that bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:18.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不運なアクシデントは！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:19.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look, there's so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:23.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,量で…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,量による必然で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's so many that I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:29.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji... Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:26.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　そうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に そういうことなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:32.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうさ　打ち破ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:30.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:32.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've smashed through!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:35.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴らの手は すべて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:36.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Through every trick they have!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてな！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:44.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,し… しかし カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:46.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あってたまるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:47.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They don't have anything left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:48.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴らに手など！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:52.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしあるなら もっと\Nさっさと出したはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:51.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If they did, they would have already used it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:55.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't hold back this long, would they!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで追い詰められてから\N出すことない　だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そりゃそうだが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:01.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:04:59.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:04.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとおりだ\Nまったく そのとおり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:05.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're right. You're exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:07.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正論さ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし あるんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:14.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But sometimes the unexpected happens and things don't go as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:14.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不測の事態\N意味不明な展開ってやつが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間の願い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:26.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Human hopes... Prayers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:28.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,願望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:31.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ambitions... All these emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:31.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,期待　そういった感情は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時に誤らせる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:34.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, they lead our minds astray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:40.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Only now does he understand what's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:37.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,認識を！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:40.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 真に何が起こっているかを！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:50.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:48.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:52.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ これ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's happening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:53.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's like a ghost dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:03.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで亡霊のダンス
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:09.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,浮遊し 乱舞するだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:09.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They waver like spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命なき銀の玉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:14.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The silver balls on which he staked his life do not strike their target!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:14.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,届かない！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:19.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次々に銀の玉が\N当たりに向かいはするが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:20.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even though they approach, they get no further!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それまで！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:23.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりには至らない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They do not strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:28.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 ただクルーン内を\N徘徊するだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:28.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They only circle in the tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:29.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バ… バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:32.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:36.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:43.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ この音？
